<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' />
    <title>Event Registration Confirmation</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style='margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;'
  >
    <table
      role='presentation'
      cellspacing='0'
      cellpadding='0'
      border='0'
      width='100%'
      style='background-color: #f4f4f4;'
    >
      <tr>
        <td style='padding: 20px 0;'>
          <!-- Main Container -->
          <table
            role='presentation'
            cellspacing='0'
            cellpadding='0'
            border='0'
            width='600'
            style='margin: 0 auto; background-color: #46270a; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;'
          >

            <!-- Header Section -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style='padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; background-color: #46270a;'
              >
                <table
                  role='presentation'
                  cellspacing='0'
                  cellpadding='0'
                  border='0'
                  width='100%'
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style='color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 10px;'
                    >
                      🎉 You're Officially In!
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style='color: #ee9d5b; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;'
                    >
                      {{eventTitle}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Welcome Message -->
            <tr>
              <td style='padding: 30px 30px 20px; background-color: #46270a;'>
                <table
                  role='presentation'
                  cellspacing='0'
                  cellpadding='0'
                  border='0'
                  width='100%'
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style='color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'
                    >
                      Hi
                      {{firstName}},<br /><br />
                      I'm so excited you signed up for our webinar
                      <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>
                      – you're officially in!<br /><br />
                      First of all, thank you for saying yes to this journey.
                      That alone is a big step.<br /><br />
                      This webinar is designed to help you start making sense of
                      the confusion you might be feeling about your purpose,
                      your next steps, or even your current season. It's going
                      to be honest, practical, and (I promise) not boring 😄
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Event Details Card -->
            <tr>
              <td style='padding: 20px 30px; background-color: #46270a;'>
                <table
                  role='presentation'
                  cellspacing='0'
                  cellpadding='0'
                  border='0'
                  width='100%'
                  style='background-color: #ee9d5b; border-radius: 8px;'
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td style='padding: 25px;'>
                      <table
                        role='presentation'
                        cellspacing='0'
                        cellpadding='0'
                        border='0'
                        width='100%'
                      >
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            style='color: #46270a; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 15px;'
                          >
                            📅 Event Details
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td style='padding: 8px 0;'>
                            <table
                              role='presentation'
                              cellspacing='0'
                              cellpadding='0'
                              border='0'
                              width='100%'
                            >
                              <tr>
                                <td
                                  style='color: #46270a; font-size: 15px; width: 60px; vertical-align: top;'
                                >
                                  🗓
                                </td>
                                <td style='color: #46270a; font-size: 15px;'>
                                  <strong>Date:</strong>
                                  {{eventDate}}
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                            </table>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td style='padding: 8px 0;'>
                            <table
                              role='presentation'
                              cellspacing='0'
                              cellpadding='0'
                              border='0'
                              width='100%'
                            >
                              <tr>
                                <td
                                  style='color: #46270a; font-size: 15px; width: 60px; vertical-align: top;'
                                >
                                  ⏰
                                </td>
                                <td style='color: #46270a; font-size: 15px;'>
                                  <strong>Time:</strong>
                                  {{eventTime}}
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                            </table>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td style='padding: 8px 0;'>
                            <table
                              role='presentation'
                              cellspacing='0'
                              cellpadding='0'
                              border='0'
                              width='100%'
                            >
                              <tr>
                                <td
                                  style='color: #46270a; font-size: 15px; width: 60px; vertical-align: top;'
                                >
                                  📍
                                </td>
                                <td style='color: #46270a; font-size: 15px;'>
                                  <strong>Venue:</strong>
                                  {{eventVenue}}
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                            </table>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Meeting Link Section -->
            {{#if meetingLink}}
              <tr>
                <td style='padding: 20px 30px; background-color: #46270a;'>
                  <table
                    role='presentation'
                    cellspacing='0'
                    cellpadding='0'
                    border='0'
                    width='100%'
                  >
                    <tr>
                      <td
                        style='color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 15px;'
                      >
                        🔗 Join the Meeting
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style='padding-bottom: 15px;'>
                        <table
                          role='presentation'
                          cellspacing='0'
                          cellpadding='0'
                          border='0'
                          width='100%'
                        >
                          <tr>
                            <td style='text-align: center; padding: 15px 0;'>
                              <a
                                href='{{meetingLink}}'
                                style='background-color: #ee9d5b; color: #46270a; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 40px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; display: inline-block;'
                              >
                                Join via Zoom
                              </a>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    {{#if meetingId}}
                      <tr>
                        <td
                          style='color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; padding: 5px 0;'
                        >
                          <strong>Meeting ID:</strong>
                          {{meetingId}}
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if meetingPasscode}}
                      <tr>
                        <td
                          style='color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; padding: 5px 0;'
                        >
                          <strong>Passcode:</strong>
                          {{meetingPasscode}}
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    {{/if}}
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
            {{/if}}

            <!-- Add to Calendar Button -->
            <tr>
              <td style='padding: 20px 30px; background-color: #46270a;'>
                <table
                  role='presentation'
                  cellspacing='0'
                  cellpadding='0'
                  border='0'
                  width='100%'
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style='color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 10px;'
                    >
                      📆 Don't miss it! Add this event to your calendar
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style='text-align: center; padding: 10px 0;'>
                      <a
                        href='{{calendarLink}}'
                        style='background-color: transparent; color: #ee9d5b; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; display: inline-block; border: 2px solid #ee9d5b;'
                      >
                        Add to Calendar
                      </a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Additional Message -->
            <tr>
              <td style='padding: 20px 30px 30px; background-color: #46270a;'>
                <table
                  role='presentation'
                  cellspacing='0'
                  cellpadding='0'
                  border='0'
                  width='100%'
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style='color: #ffffff; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic;'
                    >
                      <strong>P.S:</strong>
                      Save this email so you don't miss it!<br /><br />
                      Also, come as you are. No pressure, no perfection needed.
                      Just bring your questions, your thoughts, and an open
                      mind. That's more than enough.<br /><br />
                      I genuinely can't wait to have you in the room. It's going
                      to be a special one.
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Signature -->
            <tr>
              <td style='padding: 20px 30px 40px; background-color: #46270a;'>
                <table
                  role='presentation'
                  cellspacing='0'
                  cellpadding='0'
                  border='0'
                  width='100%'
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style='color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;'
                    >
                      See you soon 🤍<br />
                      <strong style='color: #ee9d5b;'>Bolu Taiwo</strong><br />
                      <span
                        style='color: #ee9d5b; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic;'
                      >Host</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style='padding: 20px 30px; background-color: #2d1806; text-align: center;'
              >
                <table
                  role='presentation'
                  cellspacing='0'
                  cellpadding='0'
                  border='0'
                  width='100%'
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style='color: #ee9d5b; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;'
                    >
                      This email was sent to
                      {{email}}<br />
                      If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this
                      email.
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>